extension.description:
Thank you for installing DigiStore Plugin.
To use this plugin, place the tag wherever you you want to display an "Add To Cart" button.
Basic Syntax: {digistore id=x}
Additional parameters:
align=right/left/center. For example: {digistore id=1 align=right}
quantity=yes. For example: {digistore id=1 quantity=yes}
close=yes. For example: {digistore id=1 close=yes}
Combine the parameters for complete control. For example: {digistore id=1 align=right quantity=yes close=yes}
